### =====================================================================
###  Plateforme de reconditionnement — API example calls
###  For the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client).
###  Run a request by clicking "Send Request" above each ### block.
###
###  Flow: run "Login (admin)" or "Login (client)" first — they capture
###  the JWT into @adminToken / @clientToken via the named-request refs
###  below, so the protected calls just work.
### =====================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@lang = fr

### ---------------------------------------------------------------------
### HEALTH
### ---------------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### =====================================================================
### AUTH
### =====================================================================

### Register a client (returns { token, user })
# @name registerClient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Youcef Missoum",
  "email": "client@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "telephone": "0550000000",
  "adresse": "12 rue des Ateliers, Alger"
}

### Login as client — captures the token
# @name loginClient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Login as admin (seeded via `npm run seed`) — captures the token
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@reconditionnement.fr",
  "password": "change_me"
}

### Tokens captured from the login responses above
@clientToken = {{loginClient.response.body.token}}
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

### Current identity (client)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Current identity (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### =====================================================================
### CATEGORIES
### =====================================================================

### List categories (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?lang={{lang}}

### Create a category (admin) — libelle → both columns unless libelleAr given
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "libelle": "Compresseur",
  "libelleAr": "ضاغط"
}

### Delete a category (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### =====================================================================
### COMPOSANTS — catalogue / inventory / detail / lifecycle
### =====================================================================

### Catalogue: items en vente, filtered + sorted (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/composants?etat=EN_VENTE&sort=recent&lang={{lang}}

### Catalogue with full filter set (FR-06 search + FR-07 filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/composants?etat=EN_VENTE&search=moteur&categorieId=1&type=ORGANE&marque=Bosch&qualite=BON&prixMin=100&prixMax=5000&sort=prix_asc&lang={{lang}}

### Admin inventory: omit `etat` to see every state
GET {{baseUrl}}/composants?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Composant detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/composants/1?lang={{lang}}

### Create an ORGANE (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "typeComposant": "ORGANE",
  "nom": "Moteur électrique 5kW",
  "nomAr": "محرك كهربائي 5 كيلوواط",
  "reference": "MOT-5KW-0001",
  "marque": "Bosch",
  "modele": "EM-5000",
  "categorieId": 1,
  "qualite": "TRES_BON",
  "prix": 2500.00,
  "garantie": 12,
  "images": ["https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/sample.jpg"],
  "description": "Moteur reconditionné, testé.",
  "typeEquipement": "Pompe industrielle"
}

### Create a PIECE (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "typeComposant": "PIECE",
  "nom": "Roulement à billes",
  "reference": "PCE-RLT-0001",
  "marque": "SKF",
  "categorieId": 2,
  "qualite": "COMME_NEUF",
  "prix": 80.00,
  "garantie": 6,
  "materiau": "Acier inoxydable",
  "compatibilite": "Série EM-5000"
}

### Update a composant (admin, partial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/composants/1?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prix": 2300.00,
  "qualite": "BON"
}

### Buy a composant (client) — calls acheter_composant(); 409 if already sold
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/acheter
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Declare salvageable child pieces under a parent organe (admin, FR-32)
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/pieces?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pieces": [
    {
      "nom": "Stator récupéré",
      "reference": "PCE-STA-0001",
      "prix": 0,
      "materiau": "Cuivre",
      "compatibilite": "EM-5000"
    },
    {
      "nom": "Carcasse alu",
      "reference": "PCE-CAR-0001",
      "prix": 0,
      "materiau": "Aluminium"
    }
  ]
}


### =====================================================================
### ETAPES (traçabilité)
### =====================================================================

### List a composant's traceability timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/etapes?lang={{lang}}

### Add a step (admin). ordre defaults to next slot if omitted.
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/etapes?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "DIAGNOSTIC",
  "date": "2026-06-19",
  "description": "Bobinage testé, isolement conforme."
}

### Add the terminal MISE_EN_VENTE step (FR-33: flips etat → EN_VENTE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/etapes?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "MISE_EN_VENTE",
  "date": "2026-06-19"
}

### Update a step (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/etapes/1?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Diagnostic révisé."
}

### Reorder a step up/down (admin, temp-value swap) → returns full timeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/etapes/2/reorder?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "up"
}

### Delete a step (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/etapes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### =====================================================================
### SOLD-ITEM FREEZE  (edit a VENDU composant — locked unless overridden)
###   Setup: pick a composant that is EN_VENTE, buy it as a client
###   (POST /composants/:id/acheter) so its etat_actuel becomes VENDU,
###   then run the calls below against that same id. Replace 1 / 99 as needed.
### =====================================================================

### A) Edit a SOLD composant WITHOUT override → 409 COMPOSANT_VENDU
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/composants/1?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "tentative de modification sans override"
}

### B) Edit a SOLD composant WITH override but NO motif → 400 (motif requis)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/composants/1?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "override sans motif",
  "override": true
}

### C) Edit a SOLD composant WITH override + motif → 200, audited
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/composants/1?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Correction: garantie corrigée après vente",
  "override": true,
  "motif": "Erreur de saisie sur la description, corrigée à la demande du client"
}

### D) Add a step to a SOLD composant WITHOUT override → 409 COMPOSANT_VENDU
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/etapes?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TEST",
  "description": "essai sur article vendu"
}

### E) Add a step to a SOLD composant WITH override + motif → 201, audited
POST {{baseUrl}}/composants/1/etapes?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TEST",
  "description": "Re-test après réclamation client",
  "override": true,
  "motif": "Re-test demandé par le client après livraison"
}

### F) Update a step of a SOLD composant WITHOUT override → 409 COMPOSANT_VENDU
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/etapes/99?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "modif étape sans override"
}

### G) Delete a step of a SOLD composant WITHOUT override → 409 COMPOSANT_VENDU
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/etapes/99
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### H) Delete a step of a SOLD composant WITH override + motif → 204, audited
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/etapes/99
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "override": true,
  "motif": "Étape ajoutée par erreur, retirée"
}

### I) Reorder steps of a SOLD composant WITHOUT override → 409 COMPOSANT_VENDU
POST {{baseUrl}}/etapes/99/reorder?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "up"
}

### Sanity: editing an UNSOLD (EN_VENTE) composant still works, no override needed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/composants/2?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "édition normale d'un article non vendu"
}


### =====================================================================
### OFFRES
### =====================================================================

### Submit an offer (public, FR-17) — creates entreprise + offre
POST {{baseUrl}}/offres?lang={{lang}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "designation": "Lot de moteurs hors service",
  "designationAr": "مجموعة محركات معطلة",
  "typePropose": "ORGANE",
  "marque": "Siemens",
  "modele": "SX-200",
  "reference": "LOT-2026-001",
  "categorieId": 1,
  "etatDeclare": "DEFECTUEUX",
  "prixPropose": 1200.00,
  "quantite": 5,
  "description": "5 unités, à reconditionner.",
  "images": [],
  "entreprise": {
    "nom": "Atelier Méca SARL",
    "contact": "contact@ateliermeca.dz",
    "adresse": "Zone industrielle, Oran"
  }
}

### List offers (admin), optionally filter by statut
GET {{baseUrl}}/offres?statut=EN_ATTENTE&lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Accept an offer (admin, FR-22) → fans out into N unique composants (the lot worklist).
### Omit "quantite" to accept the full offered quantity; pass it to accept a subset (one-shot partial).
POST {{baseUrl}}/offres/1/accepter?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantite": 3
}

### Reject an offer (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/offres/1/rejeter?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### =====================================================================
### FAVORIS (client)
### =====================================================================

### List favourite composants (full objects)
GET {{baseUrl}}/favoris?lang={{lang}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Add to favourites (idempotent)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/favoris/1
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### Remove from favourites
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/favoris/1
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}


### =====================================================================
### COMMANDES
### =====================================================================

### List orders — client sees own, admin sees all
GET {{baseUrl}}/commandes
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}


### =====================================================================
### UPLOADS  (auth) — multipart; returns { urls: [...] }
###   In REST Client, file paths are relative to this .http file.
### =====================================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="folder"

reconditionnement/composants
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------boundary--


### =====================================================================
### STATS (admin dashboard, FR-34)
### =====================================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
